metadata.name: Untitled #1
metadata.description:
#1 in my untitled collection. Untitled since I never know how to name things. Everyone's perceptions are different, and I don't want to take that away by putting a label on it.

This originated from an ink drawing that I did. This is my first digital artwork piece. I'm going to be creating more, with time.

This is how my abstract brain works.
